<HEADLINE> Arab League Condemns Bomb Explosion in Saudi Arabia </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CAIRO, June 26 (Xinhua) -- The Cairo-based Arab League today
strongly denounced the truck bomb explosion which occurred in
Saudi Arabia's eastern city of Dhahran Tuesday night and killed at
least 19 Americans.
</P>
<P>
