<TEXT>
<P>
OSLO, June 27 (Xinhua) -- Chinese President Jiang Zemin flew
into Oslo today from Barcelona, Spain, for a three-day state visit
to Norway at the invitation of Norwegian King Harald V.
</P>
<P>
