<HEADLINE> New York Stocks Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NEW YORK, June 26 (Xinhua) -- New York stocks were pulled down
today by another steep slide in technology issues, with the Dow
Jones industrial average fell 36.57 to 5,682.70.
</P>
