<HEADLINE> Chinese Trade Minister Visits Uruguay </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MONTEVIDEO, June 26 (Xinhua) -- China will develop trade and
economic cooperation with Uruguay and other Latin American
countries, a Chinese minister said here today.
</P>
<P>
Chinese Minister of Foreign Trade and Economic Cooperation Wu
Yi, who is heading an economic and trade delegation, held talks
with Uruguayan President Julio Maria Sanguinetti, Foreign Minister
Alvaro Ramos, and Economy and Finance Minister Luis Mosca.
</P>
<P>
