bilateral relations and cooperation in various fields and
indicated their desire to boost them.
</P>
<P>
During her four-day visit to the country, the Chinese minister,
also held talks with Uruguayan businessmen. She told them that
China wishes to expand trade and economic cooperation with Uruguay
and other Latin American countries.
</P>
<P>
Uruguay is the 6th stop of Wu's Latin American tour. She had
visited Cuba, Peru, Mexico, Chile and Argentina.
</P>
<P>
The Chinese minister left here this afternoon for Brazil to
continue her seven-nation trip. 
